  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy waves of hundreds of ships as you discover why they have contacted you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Impact Trial: First Encounter</strong> is a mix of survival <strong>Bullet Hell</strong> and non-linear sci-fi <strong>Conversational Adventure</strong> where your decisions influence the plot - you can play both modes together or separately!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > + 15 different enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 difficulty modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No combat will be the same as the previous one.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Non-linear science fiction story similar to the 70s-80s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choices influence the plot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Arcade only mode available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Available adventure only mode and full adventure mode (adventure + bullet hell).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 69 ACHIEVEMENTS!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SHUMPS - BULLET HELL</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679260/extras/fa0fcd13a62814c9a0189c6f807c9223.poster.avif?t=1760691167\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679260/extras/fa0fcd13a62814c9a0189c6f807c9223.webm?t=1760691167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679260/extras/fa0fcd13a62814c9a0189c6f807c9223.mp4?t=1760691167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p c